<title>Standards</title>
<para id="fs-idm400339248"><emphasis effect="bold">Topic</emphasis>: 3.4 Philosophical Foundations of the American Revolution</para>
<para id="fs-idm375857104"><emphasis effect="bold">Theme</emphasis>: NAT American and National Identity</para>
<para id="fs-idm397082944"><emphasis effect="bold">Learning Objective</emphasis>: Unit 3D Explain how and why colonial attitudes about government and the individual changed in the years leading up to the American Revolution</para>
