<para id="fs-idm387409872"><emphasis effect="bold">Historical Thinking Skills</emphasis>: HTS-2 Sourcing and Situation, HTS-3 Source Claims and Evidence, HTS-4 Contextualization, HTS-5 Making Connections, HTS-6 Argumentation</para>
